org.streaminer.util.hash

Class JenkinsHash

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.streaminer.util.hash.JenkinsHash

  • public class JenkinsHash
extends Object
    This is an implementation of Bob Jenkins' hash. It can produce both 32-bit and 64-bit hash values.

    Generates same hash values as the original implementation written by Bob Jenkins.
